  "description": "Installation of temporary scaffold shroud for a period of 12 months comprising 1:1 image of building facade and two externally illuminated inset advertising areas measuring 9.6m x 7.7m on the Shoreditch High Street (east) elevation and 11.7m x 7.7m on the Great Eastern Street (south) elevation.&nbsp;",
